### JWT Authentication Test - Kiểm tra toàn bộ flow

### ========================================
### BƯỚC 1: Test AuthService trực tiếp
### ========================================

### 1.1. Test AuthService - Generate Token
POST http://localhost:5060/api/auth/generate-token
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "username": "testuser"
}

### 1.2. Test AuthService - Login
POST http://localhost:5060/api/auth/login
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "username": "admin",
  "password": "password"
}

### ========================================
### BƯỚC 2: Test qua API Gateway
### ========================================

### 2.1. Test API Gateway - Generate Token (qua routing)
POST http://localhost:5050/auth/generate-token
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "username": "testuser"
}

### 2.2. Test API Gateway - Login (qua routing)
POST http://localhost:5050/auth/login
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "username": "admin",
  "password": "password"
}

### ========================================
### BƯỚC 3: Test Protected Endpoints KHÔNG có token (phải lỗi 401)
### ========================================

### 3.1. Test Pricing - GET (không có token)
GET http://localhost:5050/pricing

### 3.2. Test Pricing - GET by ID (không có token)
GET http://localhost:5050/pricing/123

### 3.3. Test Policy (không có token)
GET http://localhost:5050/policy

### ========================================
### BƯỚC 4: Test Protected Endpoints CÓ token (phải thành công)
### ========================================
### LƯU Ý: Thay YOUR_JWT_TOKEN bằng token từ bước 2.1 hoặc 2.2

### 4.1. Test Pricing - GET (có token)
GET http://localhost:5050/pricing
Authorization: Bearer YOUR_JWT_TOKEN

### 4.2. Test Pricing - GET by ID (có token)
GET http://localhost:5050/pricing/123
Authorization: Bearer YOUR_JWT_TOKEN

### 4.3. Test Pricing - POST (có token)
POST http://localhost:5050/pricing
Authorization: Bearer YOUR_JWT_TOKEN
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "basePrice": 1000,
  "quantity": 5,
  "taxRate": 0.1
}

### 4.4. Test Pricing - PUT (có token)
PUT http://localhost:5050/pricing/123
Authorization: Bearer YOUR_JWT_TOKEN
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "oldPrice": 1500,
  "newPrice": 1800
}

### 4.5. Test Pricing - DELETE (có token)
DELETE http://localhost:5050/pricing/123
Authorization: Bearer YOUR_JWT_TOKEN

### 4.6. Test Policy (có token)
GET http://localhost:5050/policy
Authorization: Bearer YOUR_JWT_TOKEN

### ========================================
### BƯỚC 5: Test với token không hợp lệ (phải lỗi 401)
### ========================================

### 5.1. Test với token giả
GET http://localhost:5050/pricing
Authorization: Bearer invalid_token_here

### 5.2. Test với token hết hạn (nếu có)
GET http://localhost:5050/pricing
Authorization: Bearer expired_token_here

### ========================================
### EXPECTED RESULTS
### ========================================
### Bước 1-2: Trả về token và thông tin user
### Bước 3: Tất cả phải trả về 401 Unauthorized
### Bước 4: Tất cả phải trả về 200 OK với data
### Bước 5: Tất cả phải trả về 401 Unauthorized